设置编译环境
设置depot_tools  获取一下google的代码获取工具
git clone https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/tools/depot_tools.git 下载失败，从别人的gitee中重新获取一个url去clone
export PATH=/root/git/depot_tools:$PATH  可以配到.bashrc

fetch --nohooks chromium 显示Running: gclient sync --nohook IOError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/root/chromium/src'
gclient sync --nohooks    失败：
                        WARNING: subprocess '"git" "-c" "core.deltaBaseCacheLimit=2g" "clone" "--no-checkout" 
                        "--progress" "https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src.git"
                        "/root/chromium/_gclient_src_OCNlh_"' in /root/chromium failed;
                         will retry after a short nap...
                       IOError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/root/chromium/src'
            此时应该生成src目录的。
不能按照这种方法下载源码，直接在github上下载。
安装依赖项 
  执行$ ./build/install-build-deps.sh 失败，提示安装lsb-release
  yum install lsb-release   又失败
运行hook 
编译